<li id="cite_note-WBtribute-9">^ <a href="#cite_ref-WBtribute_9-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-WBtribute_9-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/EXTABOUTUS/EXTARCHIVES/0,,contentMDK:20100171~pagePK:36726~piPK:36092~theSitePK:29506,00.html" class="external text" title="http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/EXTABOUTUS/EXTARCHIVES/0,,contentMDK:20100171~pagePK:36726~piPK:36092~theSitePK:29506,00.html" rel="nofollow">"Pages from World Bank History - Bank Pays Tribute to Robert McNamara"</a>. <i>Archives</i>. World Bank. March 21, 2003<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/EXTABOUTUS/EXTARCHIVES/0,,contentMDK:20100171~pagePK:36726~piPK:36092~theSitePK:29506,00.html" class="external free" title="http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/EXTABOUTUS/EXTARCHIVES/0,,contentMDK:20100171~pagePK:36726~piPK:36092~theSitePK:29506,00.html" rel="nofollow">http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/EXTABOUTUS/EXTARCHIVES/0,,contentMDK:20100171~pagePK:36726~piPK:36092~theSitePK:29506,00.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-05-26</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Pages+from+World+Bank+History+-+Bank+Pays+Tribute+to+Robert+McNamara&amp;rft.atitle=Archives&amp;rft.date=March+21%2C+2003&amp;rft.pub=World+Bank&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.worldbank.org%2FWBSITE%2FEXTERNAL%2FEXTABOUTUS%2FEXTARCHIVES%2F0%2C%2CcontentMDK%3A20100171%7EpagePK%3A36726%7EpiPK%3A36092%7EtheSitePK%3A29506%2C00.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Robert_McNamara"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
